sequenceDiagram
  actor H as Hôte
  participant UI as Interface React
  participant Auth as Firebase Auth
  participant DB as Firestore
  H->>UI: Saisir pseudo + créer salle
  UI->>Auth: signInAnonymously()
  Auth-->>UI: uid hôte
  UI->>DB: create rooms/{code}
  UI->>DB: create rooms/{code}/players/{uid}
  DB-->>UI: snapshots room + players
  UI-->>H: Afficher lobby + lien #/room/CODE
